long.am,ar,bn,de,en,en_AU,en_GB,en_US,es_419,:
It is an online HTML5 game between Dungeon. It is an interesting puzzle game among Dungeon.

You need to guide the hero to quickly clear the traps in the maze to help us escape from the maze, stop the explosives and other obstacles. Be careful to run and run, watch out for the thorny boxes that land unexpectedly when you realize nothing is happening.


To swipe Install this extension to play Among Us Dungeon or offline with no additional downloads and no ads. 

You can contact with us support@724fun.com and share your thoughts and problems

After clicking the add the game to chrome button, you can find the game in the extensions section. If you wish, you can visit zillakgames.com. If you wish, you can play again and if you want to remove it, you can remove it from the extensions section.
